OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FA personal trainer has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 14 months behind bars for causing a
OL,8,Fcrash that injured seven police
OL,9,Fofficers during a pursuit.
OL,11,FMazyar Azarbonyad, 20, who was on a
OL,12,Ffirst date at the time and has never
OL,13,Fheld a full driving licence, admitted
OL,14,Fdangerous driving following the crash
OL,15,Fon the A1 in Newcastle on 9 April.
