OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FWith the woman in the passenger seat
OL,7,Fof a dark grey BMW, he evaded police
OL,8,Fwho had tried to pull him over for a
OL,9,Fdefective light in the Swalwell area
OL,10,Fof Gateshead. Reaching speeds of over
OL,11,F100mph, he drove on to the A1 where
OL,12,Fthe major collision happened at
OL,13,Fjunction 75 near the Denton roundabout.
OL,15,FFive police vehicles were badly
OL,16,Fdamaged and some officers had to be
OL,17,Fcut from the car. Seven were taken to
OL,18,Fhospital and prosecutor Jolyon Perks
OL,19,Fsaid it was "truly remarkable" they
OL,20,Fdid not suffer more serious injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
