OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FHe added: "A number of these officers
OL,7,Fwere trapped in vehicles. There were
OL,8,Fliquids involved, thankfully not
OL,9,Fpetrol. A number of officers were
OL,10,Frendered unconscious. It was clearly a
OL,11,Fvery traumatic incident."
OL,13,FOne officer suffered soft tissue
OL,14,Fdamage to her knee and nerve damage to
OL,15,Fher back, requiring her to remain in
OL,16,Fhospital for three days, and another
OL,17,Fneeded stitches for a cut to his
OL,18,Fforehead, the court heard. Four
OL,19,Fofficers remain off work as a result
OL,20,Fof the collision.
