OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FThe road was closed for most of the
OL,7,Fday causing "traffic chaos" across
OL,8,FTyneside.
OL,10,FAzarbonyad also admitted two counts of
OL,11,Ffailing to stop, driving without a
OL,12,Flicence and insurance.
OL,14,FAfter he was released on police bail
OL,15,Ffollowing the A1 incident, he
OL,16,Fcontinued to drive from Stanley,
OL,17,FCounty Durham, to a Newcastle city
OL,18,Fcentre gym where he worked and police
OL,19,Fspotted him filling up his car on a
OL,20,Fgarage forecourt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
