OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FAzarbonyad faced further offences of
OL,7,Fdriving without insurance or a licence
OL,8,Fon April 16, seven days after the
OL,9,Fcrash.
OL,11,FPenny Hall, defending, said Azarbonyad
OL,12,F"panicked" after his passenger told
OL,13,Fhim she had drugs on her.
OL,15,FShe said the defendant, of Sylvia
OL,16,FTerrace, Stanley, County Durham,
OL,17,Ftravelled to the UK from Iran with his
OL,18,Funcle, but lost him during the journey
OL,19,Fand had never seen him again.
