OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FAfter time in immigration centres and
OL,7,Ffoster placements he was granted leave
OL,8,Fto remain and refugee status, the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FMs Hall told the court: "Quite
OL,12,Ffrankly, he is terrified at the
OL,13,Fprospect of going to prison."
OL,15,FSentencing him at Newcastle Crown
OL,16,FCourt, Judge Tim Gittins said: "It is
OL,17,Fnothing short of a miracle that no one
OL,18,Fwas more seriously injured or that
OL,19,Fthere were not multiple fatalities.
