OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,F"It led to regional traffic chaos,
OL,7,Fmisery for many travellers, not to
OL,8,Fmention the substantial loss of work
OL,9,Fand study hours for those that were
OL,10,Fcaught up in the aftermath of what you
OL,11,Fcaused."
OL,13,FAzarbonyad will serve his sentence in
OL,14,Fa young offenders institute. The judge
OL,15,Fsaid he would be expected to serve 40%
OL,16,Fof his sentence.
