OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,FHe has been banned from driving for
OL,7,Fthree years and seven months which
OL,8,Fwill begin when he is released. He
OL,9,Fmust also sit an extended test to
OL,10,Fdrive lawfully in the future.
OL,12,FFollowing the sentencing, Northumbria
OL,13,FPolice Superintendent Billy Mulligan
OL,14,Fsaid: "It is sheer luck that Mazyar
OL,15,FAzarbonyad did not kill anyone that
OL,16,Fday with his reckless actions.
OL,18,F"What should have been a simple stop
OL,19,Fturned into him driving incredibly
OL,20,Fdangerously in a bid to get away from
OL,21,Fofficers.
OL,26,@vD@GOUzD@AOU
