OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,F"He showed absolutely zero regard for
OL,7,Fthe safety of anyone else that
OL,8,Fmorning, and his decision-making
OL,9,Fbehind the wheel put lives at risk.
OL,11,F"I would like to recognise the bravery
OL,12,Fof the officers involved in the
OL,13,Fpursuit and subsequent collision on
OL,14,Fthe A1.
OL,16,F"While three officers have been able
OL,17,Fto return to duty, four of our
OL,18,Fcolleagues remain off work ` and I
OL,19,Fwish them all the best in their
OL,20,Frecovery.
