OL,3,CDriver sentenced for causing A1 crash
OL,4,Cwhich injured seven police officers
OL,6,F"They were simply doing their job,
OL,7,Fprotecting the public from the actions
OL,8,Fof someone who was not even qualified
OL,9,For insured to drive.
OL,11,F"We have a zero-tolerance approach to
OL,12,Fthis type of behaviour, and we are
OL,13,Fcommitted to bringing offenders to
OL,14,Fjustice and ensuring our roads as safe
OL,15,Fas possible."
